Program: Outlook
Title: Outlook Weekend: How Was Your Holiday?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p059zb9q
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 7 Aug 2017
Star Trek actor, George Takei was told by his parents that he was going on a holiday but instead he ended up spending his childhood in a US internment camp. Karl Williams is a musician from London who goes by the name of 'Ceaser London'. In 2012 he went on a lads' holiday to Dubai to celebrate the birth of his daughter but he and his friends were arrested and sent to prison. Image: Girl with a suitcase standing on a jetty Credit: fcscafeine/iStock /Getty Images Plus Show less